Equora — The Trust Layer for Group Payments

Split bills. Verify payments. Eliminate “bro I already paid” forever.

Equora is a high-speed, transparency-first settlement engine built for modern group payments.

It combines:

⚡ Instant bill splitting
💸 UPI-powered payment flow
🔗 Algorand on-chain verification
📊 Proof-backed settlement tracking

No spreadsheets. No confusion. No arguments.

🧠 The Problem

Group payments today are chaos:

“I sent you bro” (no proof)
Wrong splits and manual calculations
Endless screenshots in WhatsApp
No single source of truth

Result?
Time wasted. Trust broken. Settlements delayed.

🚀 The Solution

Equora replaces messy coordination with a structured + verifiable system:

Every bill is calculated automatically
Every payment has a status + proof
Every group has a clear settlement state

And most importantly:

🔐 Payments can be verified on-chain using Algorand

