📲 UPI Payment Flow (Frictionless UX)
graph TD
A[Create Bill] --> B[Split Among Members]
B --> C[Generate Payment Requests]
C --> D[Pay via UPI]
D --> E[Mark Paid OR Verify via Algorand]
E --> F[Update Status Board]
F --> G[View Settlement Suggestions]
G --> H[Ledger Stores Proof]
Deep link → opens GPay / PhonePe instantly
QR support for fast payments
